'Tonight you shall sleep in peace.'
'You know not what you say. There is in her and in this land no evil, unless a man bring it hither himself. Then let him beware! But tonight I shall sleep without fear for the first time since I left Rivendell. And may I sleep deep, and forget for a while my grief! I am weary in body and in heart.'
`You did not wish to see Elf-magic and were content.'
`I will give you the One Ring, if you ask for it. It is too great a matter for me.'
